{"tid":1044600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大民主牆風波　「我會願諒你」事件","createTime":"2019-03-03T04:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T00:37:53.000Z","uid":47714,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"06c8c256ce734cd98ecf2f9f135dcffe159798b3","tid":1044600,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156516942131773&amp;set=a.10150830093141773&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156516942131773%26set%3Da.10150830093141773%26type%3D3&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyED%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=c71c1f3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156516942131773&amp;set=a.10150830093141773&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\nMung Siu Tat:<br />\n<br />\n［我會原諒你］<br />\n<br />\n混亂中，教授突然單腳跌在地上，何同學即時上前扶起，緊張地問：「你有無事？有無事？需唔需要搵個地方坐低？」<br />\n<br />\n教授猶豫了一陣，表示沒事，並用手搭著何同學膊頭，連聲表示「我會原諒你」、「我會原諒你」，何同學卻向對方說：「我唔係要你原諒我，我係唔會原諒校方打壓民主自由！」<br />\n<br />\n教授隨即澄清：「我係話我會原諒你整親我隻腳」。<br />\n<br />\n看到這裡，想到何同學嘅下場，我心裡都寒了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/211443_00fb7f2091cff6afb826ded61cd6049a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F211443_00fb7f2091cff6afb826ded61cd6049a.jpg&h=ad91b3c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWayne Baradian Chan 有無原片<br />\n<br />\nMung Siu Tat <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/理大前學生會長被勒令停學一年-去年民主牆衝突阻高層離開/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%89%8D%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%E8%A2%AB%E5%8B%92%E4%BB%A4%E5%81%9C%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E7%89%86%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E9%98%BB%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%2F&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyED%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=6a205fe8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%89%8D%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%E8%A2%AB%E5%8B%92%E4%BB%A4%E5%81%9C%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E7%89%86%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E9%98%BB%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%2F&h=16d6a8f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/理大前學生會長被勒令停學一年-去年民主牆衝突阻高層離開/</a><br />\n<br />\nWayne Baradian Chan 我想搵一搵段片 , 可能遲啲做法律理據<br />\n<br />\nMung Siu Tat 立場篇報導裡頭有<br />\n<br />\nWayne Baradian Chan 見到了，感謝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLucy Bebe 乜那野教授咁仆街去屈學生！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTse Charles 學院界岳不群<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安格斯 盧寵茂教嘅？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文芳儀 真係好仆街！人哋係佢右邊行過，佢竟然話人撞到佢隻左腳。做戲都唔好咁假啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張堅利<br />\n呢個所謂教授相信係大陸嚟㗎<br />\n佢用呢招&quot;碰瓷&quot;實在爐火純青<br />\n睇見佢嘅眼神根本就係話俾你知<br />\n你班細路原全未夠班同佢鬥陰毒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張堅利 經典已成始祖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/041046_a7c45a6a69f11ab8e61333208ace2d94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F041046_a7c45a6a69f11ab8e61333208ace2d94.jpg&h=884fd6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKim O Dan 下流撞車黨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JNVJEg5H8xg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJNVJEg5H8xg&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyED%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=7f2f5efd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JNVJEg5H8xg</a>"},{"pid":"7554e7d1143bd51018a4e5d88b77d0faca5957b4","tid":1044600,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yip